Subject:Re: [Flexradio] Upgrading XP to windows 7
One thing I recommend is to upgrade the firmware on the SSD before loading the OS. There should be instructions on the manufacturer's web site. Depending on manufacturer and current version of firmware you might see a significant performance improvement. 

Dave
wo2x

